| Comment: Persistence via Scheduled Task Creation
| Comment: Detects creation of scheduled tasks, a common persistence mechanism
| Comment: MITRE ATT&CK Tags: attack.persistence, attack.t1053.005, attack.privilege_escalation
index=windows sourcetype=WinEventLog:Security
| search (Image="*\schtasks.exe" AND CommandLine="*/create*") OR (Image="*\at.exe") OR (Image="*\schtasks.exe" AND CommandLine="*/xml*")
| table _time, host, user, CommandLine, Image, EventID
| sort -_time